        .default-text
          h2 Premise

          p Millions of animals are currently in shelters and foster homes awaiting adoption. Design an experience that will help connect people looking for a new pet with the right companion for them. Help an adopter find a pet which matches their lifestyle, considering factors including breed, gender, age, temperament, and health status. Provide a high-level flow and supporting wire frames.
          
          hr

          h2 What do people feel about the adoption process?

          p I started by reading extensively about how people approach the task of buying a pet, in their own words.

          p The web is full of thousands of conversations with pet owners, animal activists, and people curious about the process of buying a pet. I spent a few hours visiting as many corners as I could, getting varied perspectives, and compiling quotes that encapsulated people's thoughts, fears, and motivations.

          p These quotes were tagged by topic, and from there I compiled a summary of recurring themes.

