      .default-text(style="padding-top: 0;")
        h2 Questionnaire: The basics
        p The account experience here is intentionally unintrusive. A first name for use when messaging sellers is all that's required. Payment info, etc can be deferred until later on. 
        p The first few questions knock out the major points - breeder vs shelter, puppy vs adult, and sex. The "no preference" selectors are larger to steer users in the direction of most possible results.
      .row
