        h2 Questionnaire: Home life
        p These questions paint a picture of home life, which is useful when evaulating what types of dogs will enjoy a property, and which sellers are likely to consider a property sufficient for a given dog.
        p The selections here compound visually - the user's home selection is the backdrop as they describe their family, which is the backdrop as they describe their current pets.
